text:
<@U05KW1T3HBQ> 無限ループが起きています。修正せよ
```'use client'
import { useAtom } from 'jotai'
import { UserProduct } from '@/src/infra/api/@types/index'
import { getUserProducts } from '@/src/infra/repository/userProduct'
import { userAtom } from '@/store/user'
import { UserProductCardMobile } from '../../__components__/Product/UserProductCardMobile.client'

const dataFetch = async (userId: number, userUid: string): Promise<UserProduct[]> => {
  try {
    return await getUserProducts({ userId, userUid })
  } catch (err) {
    return []
  }
}

export const UserProductsListMobile = ({ userId }: { userId: number }) => {
  const [user, setUser] = useAtom(userAtom)
  try {
    const results = dataFetch(userId, user?.uid ?? '').then((_results) => {
      if (_results.length)
        return (
          <>
            <span className='m-4 flex justify-end'>
              {_results.length}件/{_results.length}件
            </span>
            <span className='grid grid-cols-1 gap-2'>
              {_results.map((result: UserProduct, index: number) => (
                <div key={index} className='flex justify-center'>
                  <div className='flex-1'>
                    <UserProductCardMobile
                      imageSrc={result.imageUrl ?? ''}
                      title={result.name ?? ''}
                      brand={result.brand ?? ''}
                      repeats={result.repeats ?? 0}
                      usingSince={result.registeredAt ?? ''}
                      discontinued={result.discontinuedOn ? true : false}
                    />
                  </div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </span>
          </>
        )
      else {
        return (
          <div className='flex justify-center'>
            <div className='w-3/4'>所持品情報はありませんでした。</div>
          </div>
        )
      }
    })
    return <div className='search-results'>{results}</div>
  } catch (e) {
    console.debug(e)
    return <>エラーが発生しました。時間をおいてから再度読み込んでください。</>
  }
}```
